{"tid":409630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<維持現狀>南韓總統文在寅：首爾不尋求北韓垮台","createTime":"2017-09-22T08:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T10:21:29.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45dd66ec62183bc8016fca4be28aa5f8962a1029","tid":409630,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:26:27.000Z","msg":"文在寅：首爾不尋求北韓垮台<br />\n<br />\n2017-09-22 01:05<br />\n<br />\n南韓總統文在寅今天在聯合國大會發表演說時表示，首爾當局不尋求北韓垮台，並敦請各方致力緩和緊張局勢。<br />\n<br />\n長期抱持鴿派立場的文在寅警告北韓，務必要終結一連串核試和飛彈試射，但也承諾如果北韓作出改變，南韓願意提供協助。文在寅指：「我們不希望北韓垮台，倘若北韓做出站在歷史正確一方的決定，我們已準備好與國際社會攜手協助北韓。」<br />\n<br />\n文在寅未直接批評美國總統特朗普，而是呼籲各方冷靜。特朗普於兩天前在聯大首度發表演說時，揚言要「徹底摧毀」北韓。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1019486/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1019486%2F&d=w4d6%2BSG2rwswpfweG4w1KdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=971f3f31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1019486%2F&h=5b301950\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1019486/</a>"},{"pid":"305fb68095517e4588f7473a8a963087cb3ac12c","tid":409630,"uid":26389,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:27:44.000Z","msg":"呢條on9都做到總統"},{"pid":"d5ad0d4bf65b9ad79adcb4d4725ae2a769d60bc1","tid":409630,"uid":53660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:27:56.000Z","msg":"死左膠"},{"pid":"924e7f4e48f52b3936ecd38d46845f559f59fc90","tid":409630,"uid":42767,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:28:39.000Z","msg":"南韓一向立場都係咁, 無咩好奇怪<br />\n要消化北韓咁多窮人? 不了"},{"pid":"b03cb07aac1c7078446e84294e13996b5aeabed2","tid":409630,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />苙水了"},{"pid":"990bb79797b27220ccd331b69a1a965290db0e81","tid":409630,"uid":42586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sc